defaultWritten evidence to the Enquiry into Democracy and Development in Burma, submitted by the Burma Relief CentredefaultSummarydefaultThis submission by Burma Relief Centre, an NGO with 25 years’ experience in capacity building of civil society and currently receiving DFID support through Christian Aid, contains the following key points:
