default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultTo enable them to raise community concerns and input policy recommendations into political negotiations so that just, sustainable solutions can be achieved to end the conflict.   
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultTo ensure that humanitarian needs in these conflict areas continue to be met, and existing community social service structures are built upon and not ignored and replaced. 
